ug":["fr","texts","alice-in-wonderland"],"hidden":false,"title":"Alice in Wonderland","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","how-the-enemy-came-to-thlunrana"],"hidden":false,"title":"Comment l'Ennemi est venu à Thlunrana","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","in-a-bitter-hour"],"hidden":false,"title":"In A Bitter Hour","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","jokes"],"hidden":false,"title":"Blagues","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","lords-prayer"],"hidden":false,"title":"Lord's prayer","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","navy-seal-copypasta"],"hidden":false,"title":"Navy Seal Copypasta","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","terry-the-tiger-visits-the-big-city"],"hidden":false,"title":"Terry le tigre visite la grande ville","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","the-bad-beginning"],"hidden":false,"title":"The Bad Beginning","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","the-book"],"hidden":false,"title":"Le Livre","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","the-girl-from-ipanema"],"hidden":false,"title":"The Girl from Ipanema","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","the-mask"],"hidden":false,"title":"Le Masque","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","the-north-wind-and-the-sun"],"hidden":false,"title":"Le vent du nord et le soleil","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","there-will-come-soft-rains"],"hidden":false,"title":"Il y aura de douces pluies","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts","to-kill-a-child"],"hidden":false,"title":"Tuer un enfant","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","texts"],"hidden":false,"title":"📚 Corpus de textes","directory":"fr"},{"slug":["fr","welcome"],"hidden":false,"title":"Qu'est-ce que le Lojban ?","directory":"fr"}],"currentLanguage":"fr","post":{"slug":["fr","articles","live_chat"],"title":"💬 Chat","hidden":false,"content":"<p>Lojban est une langue vivante, et vous pouvez contacter des experts en Lojban dans un chat.</p>\n<p>La communauté de Lojban utilise un chat unifié. Vous pouvez utiliser l'un des messagers populaires suivants et vos messages seront envoyés depuis le messager que vous utilisez vers les canaux respectifs dans tous les autres messagers. Nous utilisons un programme \"pont\" spécial pour y parvenir.</p>\n<p>Choisissez le messager que vous préférez.</p>\n<h3 id=\"-lojban---lojban\"><img src=\"https://github.com/La-Lojban/suho-pixra-pe-la-jbotcan/blob/master/logo-24.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\"> #lojban - \"Lojban\"<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#-lojban---lojban\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>Le chat principal est enregistré publiquement : toutes les questions</p>\n<p>Rejoindre via un messager gratuit : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"-ckule---école\"><img src=\"https://github.com/La-Lojban/suho-pixra-pe-la-jbotcan/blob/master/jduli-24.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\"> #ckule - \"École\"<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#-ckule---école\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>Un chat où vous posez des questions sur Lojban et obtenez des réponses de locuteurs compétents et couramment.</p>\n<p>Fait amusant : ceci est le symbole de la gelée appelée <strong>lo jduli</strong> en Lojban (prononcé comme <em>loh zhdooh-leeh</em>), qui rime avec <strong>lo ckule</strong>, école (<em>loh shkooh-leh</em>)</p>\n<p>Rejoindre via un messager gratuit : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"jbosnu---discussions-uniquement-en-lojban\">#jbosnu - Discussions uniquement en Lojban<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#jbosnu---discussions-uniquement-en-lojban\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>Un chat pour discuter uniquement en Lojban</p>\n<p>Rejoindre via un messager gratuit : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"jboselbau---discussions-hors-sujet\">#jboselbau - Discussions hors sujet<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#jboselbau---discussions-hors-sujet\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>Un chat pour discuter uniquement en Lojban.</p>\n<p>Rejoindre via un messager gratuit : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://telegram.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"voknoi---échange-de-messages-vocaux\">#voknoi - Échange de messages vocaux<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#voknoi---échange-de-messages-vocaux\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>Rejoindre via un messager gratuit : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n","fullPath":"/app/src/md_pages/fr/articles/live_chat.md","toc":[{"depth":"3","value":" #lojban - \"Lojban\"","id":"-lojban---lojban","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":" #ckule - \"École\"","id":"-ckule---école","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":"#jbosnu - Discussions uniquement en Lojban","id":"jbosnu---discussions-uniquement-en-lojban","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":"#jboselbau - Discussions hors sujet","id":"jboselbau---discussions-hors-sujet","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":"#voknoi - Échange de messages vocaux","id":"voknoi---échange-de-messages-vocaux","tagName":"h3"}],"imgs":[]}},"__N_SSG":true}